com.artisan.incodeapi
Class ExperimentDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.artisan.incodeapi.ExperimentDetails
Direct Known Subclasses:
InCodeExperimentDetails, PowerHookExperimentDetails
public class ExperimentDetails
extends java.lang.Object

Represents an experiment, including its name and variants.

Instead of creating ExperimentDetails objects directly, it's better to use the methods defined in ArtisanExperimentManager.
